snippet.textDisplay: Jhule Lal=== This is what Strings is about.. "Experimenting Successfully", At first you compare the song with the previous renditions but as soon as you are over the comparison you find the brave and yet perfectly blended version of strings Dumadam Mast Qalandar is a bliss to hear especially when towards the end you yourself are singing the song with QB, she puts in her best as a powerful yet soulful singer backed by the amazing voice of Arieb Azhar.. a true genius by Strings to bring in the Humnava to retain the sufi element in entirety... Amazing Track..
